OL,3,CEvri announces partnership with
OL,4,Cdisability charity Scope
OL,6,FParcel delivery firm Evri has
OL,7,Fannounced a partnership with
OL,8,Fdisability equality charity Scope
OL,9,Faimed at improving doorstep deliveries
OL,10,Ffor people with a condition or
OL,11,Fimpairment.
OL,13,FMore options will be offered for those
OL,14,Fwho might need longer, or who can't
OL,15,Fget to the door to accept a delivery.
