OL,3,CEvri announces partnership with
OL,4,Cdisability charity Scope
OL,6,FEvri, which said it estimated that one
OL,7,Fin four home deliveries go to people
OL,8,Fwith a disability, has entered into a
OL,9,Fthree-year partnership with Scope,
OL,10,Fincluding a #125,000 donation to
OL,11,Fsupport the charity's work.
OL,13,FThe initiative includes the ability
OL,14,Ffor disabled people to request more
OL,15,Ftime to get to the door and to ring
OL,16,Fthe doorbell instead of knocking.
