OL,3,CEvri announces partnership with
OL,4,Cdisability charity Scope
OL,6,FMartijn de Lange, Evri's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, Evri, said: "Our own
OL,8,Fresearch shows that one in four people
OL,9,Frely on home deliveries to maintain
OL,10,Ftheir independence or improve the
OL,11,Fquality of their life.
OL,13,F"We are launching exciting new product
OL,14,Fdevelopments which will improve
OL,15,Fservices for those with accessibility
OL,16,Fneeds."
