OL,6,FAmanda Mitchell, executive director of
OL,7,Ffundraising at Scope, said: "There are
OL,8,F16 million disabled people in the UK,
OL,9,Freflecting a huge proportion of Evri's
OL,10,Fcustomers and workforce."Our
OL,11,Femployment experts will be working
OL,12,Fwith Evri to support them in becoming
OL,13,Fa more accessible and inclusive
OL,14,Fbusiness for their employees and
OL,15,Fcustomers.
