OL,3,CEvri announces partnership with
OL,4,Cdisability charity Scope
OL,6,F"We are encouraged that Evri is
OL,7,Fprioritising addressing disability
OL,8,Finequality in its business and is
OL,9,Fcommitted to learning and improving
OL,10,Fits practices. It's only by working
OL,11,Ftogether that we will achieve real
OL,12,Fsocial change and can create an equal
OL,13,Ffuture for disabled people."
OL,15,FLisa Webb, Which? consumer law expert,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Which? research previously
OL,17,Ffound that seven in 10 disabled
OL,18,Fconsumers who used a delivery firm had
OL,19,Ffaced problems, so it's positive to
OL,20,Fsee Evri taking steps to improve their
OL,21,Fdoorstep delivery experience.
